p://www.npc.gov.cn/npc/xinwen/2018-06/12/content_2055873.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.npc.gov.cn%2Fnpc%2Fxinwen%2F2018-06%2F12%2Fcontent_2055873.htm&d=qAjeUnq431rM%2BBBwyK7HkTACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=ebcbe550\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.npc.gov.cn/npc/xinwen/2018-06/12/content_2055873.htm</a><br />\n第十條　國家情報工作機構根據工作需要，依法使用必要的方式、手段和渠道，在境內外開展情報工作。<br />\n<br />\n第十四條　國家情報工作機構依法開展情報工作，可以要求有關機關、組織和公民提供必要的支持、協助和配合。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中興同華為一定有黨委，即係支共爪牙，而家無風險唔代表聽日無"},{"pid":"0aaca2b4b9c8a0859f08fd6765baa93fcafffe50","tid":946459,"uid":25055,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T15:07:45.000Z","msg":"華為d 晶片都唔係佢地做<br />\n只係買人貨再組裝 就叫搞5G"},{"pid":"7685e250d933809236d41b863952aec83365a3d9","tid":946459,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T15:16:18.000Z","msg":"美國有晒司諾登既證據咪又係無事<br />\n<br />\n痴孖根走去講証據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b73d067a142ca81fc8fbf92ade6b5708efb355","tid":946459,"uid":12628,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T15:22:06.000Z","msg":"比左啲基站佢起，同用佢啲通訊設備，佢平時可以扮正經唔拎係資料，但佢需求偷係資料時，就隨時都拎得，咁樣大開中門比個賊，有咩安全可言"}]}